    {
      "kind": "parameters",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "A  rendering context.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "ctx"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The font ID associated with the font whose character glyphs you want to use. The ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "fontID",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " value can identify any font family that is valid for passing into the TextFont function.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "fontID"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The font style. The ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "face",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " value can be any valid style that can be passed into the TextFace function.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "face"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The font size.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "size"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The index of the first glyph to use.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "first"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The number of glyphs to use.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "count"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The index of the first display list to generate.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "base"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return-value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Returns ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "GL_FALSE",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " if it fails for any reason, ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "GL_TRUE",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " otherwise. If an error occurs, call the function ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglGetError",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to determine what the error is.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A display list contains one or more OpenGL commands that are stored and available to be executed later by your application. The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "aglUseFont",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function generates a set of display lists, each of which contains a single call to the OpenGL ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "glBitmap",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function. AGL generates names for each display list by using the value  specified in the  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "base",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " parameter and increasing sequentially to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "base",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " + ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "count – 1",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The prototype for the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "glBitmap",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function is :",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "void glBitmap(GLsizei width,",
            "            GLsizei height,",
            "            GLfloat xorig,",
            "            GLfloat yorig,",
            "            GLfloat xmove,",
            "            GLfloat ymove,",
            "            const GLubyte *bitmap)",
            " "
          ],
          "syntax": "objc",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "AGL generates parameters for each ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "glBitmap",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " command in each display list using the following rules:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The formatting parameters—",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "xorig",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "yorig",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "width",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", and ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "height",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "—are computed from the font metrics provided in the font as ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "0",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", font descent – 1, font width, and font ascent + descent, respectively.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "xmove",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " parameter based on the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "width",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " metric of the glyph.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "ymove",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " is set to ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "0",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The glyph image is converted to the appropriate format for the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "bitmap",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " parameter.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "AGL creates empty display lists for all glyphs that you request and that are not defined in the font. For current fonts, see the file ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "fonts.h",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information on the  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "glBitmap",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function see the OpenGL Reference Manual.  You might also want to look at the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "glNewList",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function, which is the function that AGL uses to generate the display lists.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
